name: .E_E File Extension
summary: Learn about .E_E files and view a list of programs that open them.

description: Windows executable (.EXE) file that has been renamed with the ".e_e" extension, possibly to escape being filtered by an email program that detects file attachments with the ".exe" extension.

content: E_E files can be renamed with the ".exe" extension and run, but they should not be run if you do not know the source of the file, since it is possible that it contains a virus, especially if it was transmitted over email.
